data.script:
create vertex Role set roleId = 'blogAdmin', description = 'Blog Admin'
create vertex Role set roleId = 'forumAdmin', description = 'Forum Admin'
create vertex Role set roleId = 'newsAdmin', description = 'News Admin'
let blogAdmin = create vertex MenuItem set menuItemId = 'blogAdmin', text = 'Blog Admin', route = '/admin/blogAdmin', roles = 'blogAdmin,admin,owner'
let forumAdmin = create vertex MenuItem set menuItemId = 'forumAdmin', text = 'Forum Admin', route = '/admin/forumAdmin', roles = 'forumAdmin,admin,owner'
let newsAdmin = create vertex MenuItem set menuItemId = 'newsAdmin', text = 'News Admin', route = '/admin/newsAdmin', roles = 'newsAdmin,admin,owner'
let blog = create vertex MenuItem set menuItemId = 'blog', text = 'Blog', route = '/blog', roles = 'anonymous,user'
let forum = create vertex MenuItem set menuItemId = 'forum', text = 'Forum', route = '/forum', roles = 'anonymous,user'
let news = create vertex MenuItem set menuItemId = 'news', text = 'News', route = '/news', roles = 'anonymous,user'
let admin = select from MenuItem where menuItemId = 'admin'
create edge Own from $admin to $blogAdmin
create edge Own from $admin to $forumAdmin
create edge Own from $admin to $newsAdmin
let main = select from MenuItem where menuItemId = 'main'
create edge Own from $main to $blog
create edge Own from $main to $forum
create edge Own from $main to $news
